Jaan Nisar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

7th Sky Entertainment‚Äôs mega project, Jaan Nisar, is the most awaited drama serial of the year.
The highly anticipated project marks the return of the successful on-screen couple of Danish Taimoor and Hiba Bukhari in an unforgettable love story that will steal your heart.

Nosherwan Ghaznavi, a wealthy young man, faces a pivotal moment in his life after his brother's death. This tragedy burdens Nosherwan Ghaznavi with numerous responsibilities, which he reluctantly accepts, only to find them later proving detrimental. However, his life takes a transformative turn upon meeting Dua, falling in love with her at first sight, but it places him at a critical juncture with his responsibilities.

Dua, a beautiful girl from a humble background, is raised by her parents alongside her two sisters. Despite her innocence, fate subjects Dua to a string of misfortunes before encountering Nosherwan Ghaznavi. However, their meeting completely changes their lives.

Will Nowsherwan Ghaznavi find love? What challenges will he face in balancing his duties and his love for Dua? Will his responsibilities jeopardize his love for Dua? What past events have shaped Dua's life, and will they resurface to trouble her? Will Dua return Nowsherwan Ghaznavi‚Äôs love?

It also co stars Meenakshi Chowdary, Nora Fatehi, Naveen Chandra and others. Music by GV Prakash Kumar, Cinematography by A Kishor Kumar and Proudly Produced on a massive scale by Dr. Vijender Reddy Teegala and Rajani Talluri under Vyra Entertainments in Association with SRT Entertainments

en-IN.description:
Get ready for a high-octane experience with the action-packed teaser of  #Matka! Featuring Varun Tej, Meenakshi Chowdary, and Nora Fatehi, with a powerful soundtrack by GV Prakash Kumar, directed by Karuna Kumar. A thrilling treat awaits!

Stay updated with the latest videos, Subscribe on the link - http://bit.ly/adityamusic
Click here to share on Facebook- https://bit.ly/3v3iHeg  

#MATKA is an upcoming Periodical Film starring Mega Prince Varun tej in the Lead Role, Written and Directed by Karuna Kumar. It also co stars Meenakshi Chowdary, Nora Fatehi, Naveen Chandra and others. Music by GV Prakash Kumar, Cinematography by A Kishor Kumar and Proudly Produced on a massive scale by Dr. Vijender Reddy Teegala and Rajani Talluri under Vyra Entertainments in Association with SRT Entertainments

The story which takes place between 1958-1982 is based on a real incident that shook the entire nation and the story is set in the backdrop of Vizag. The story spans 24 years. 

Cast: #VarunTej, #MeenakshiChowdary, #NoraFatehi, Naveen Chandra, Kannada Kishore, Ajay Ghosh, Mime Gopi, Roopalakshmi, Vijayrama Raju, Jagadeesh, Raj Thirandas.

Kaffara Episode 79 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 7th October 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. However, due to a conspiracy, objections arise about their closeness. Salar, once again, avoids the issue, leaving Sitara to face doubts from her own family.
Can Sitara prove she‚Äôs not guilty? Will Salar help her avoid further mistreatment? Will her family support Sitara? Can Salar show he genuinely cares? Will there be more plots against Sitara?

Kaffara Episode 78 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 6th October 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. However, due to a conspiracy, objections arise about their closeness. Salar, once again, avoids the issue, leaving Sitara to face doubts from her own family.
Can Sitara prove she‚Äôs not guilty? Will Salar help her avoid further mistreatment? Will her family support Sitara? Can Salar show he genuinely cares? Will there be more plots against Sitara?

Kaffara Episode 78 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 6th October 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. However, due to a conspiracy, objections arise about their closeness. Salar, once again, avoids the issue, leaving Sitara to face doubts from her own family.
Can Sitara prove she‚Äôs not guilty? Will Salar help her avoid further mistreatment? Will her family support Sitara? Can Salar show he genuinely cares? Will there be more plots against Sitara?

snippet.description:
Filmymoji Middle Class Madhu Ganesh Master Velli Vastha Climax Episode MCM
Filmymoji Kannada :- https://www.youtube.com/@FilmymojiKannada-y3x
"In this Filmymoji  Middle Class Madhu episode, Madhu and his friends are sitting in the pandiri (a gathering spot) chatting when they receive a message from the principal's office. The principal orders them to clean up the premises immediately, leaving everyone disappointed. They return to the pandiri and discuss their bond with Ganesh Master, telling him that if he needs anything, the Nattugunta gang is always there for him. Later, a boy who can't afford the fees decides to commit suicide by going to the top floor, but Madhu and friends rescue him and set out to clean up the premises. What happens next is what makes this episode a delightful mix of comedy and emotion. Watch this episode to enjoy."

snippet.title: TUTTI FRUTTI | Colourful Papaya Candy with Ice Cream | Papaya Harvesting and Cooking in Village
snippet.description:
Today, we cook a colorful Tutti Frutti recipe using farm-fresh raw papaya. Tutti Frutti is a sweet candy made from papaya, which is also used for baking. We harvest fresh papaya from the Papaya farm to make the colorful Tutti Frutti candy.

Finally, We eat this Tutti Frutti with Ice Cream! Yummy!

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS |  Real Madrid 2-0 Villarreal | LaLiga 2024/25
snippet.description:
Real Madrid will head into the international break having taken all three points against third-placed Villarreal at the Bernab√©u. Ancelotti's men secured the win with two superb strikes from outside the box. The first was by Valverde after a well-rehearsed move from a corner-kick. On the quarter-hour mark, Modriƒá took a short corner, Bellingham tricked the defence by letting the ball run past him and Valverde did the rest. The Uruguayan hit a fierce first-time strike from outside the area which flew past Diego Conde with the help of a deflection off Baena. In the second half and Vini Jr. scored with a spectacular right-footed finish. In the 70th minute, the Brazilian picked up the ball on the edge of the box and swerved a strike into the top corner giving Diego Conde no chance.Madrid extended their unbeaten run in LaLiga to 41 games (30 wins and 11 draws). The downside came in stoppage time when Carvajal was stretchered off in considerable pain and received a standing ovation from the home fans.
#RealMadridVillarreal | #LaLigaHighlights

Dr. Salunke's examination of the deceased's body reveals something unusual. Despite the appearance of a heart attack, Dr. Salunke detects signs of foul play that indicate the death was not natural. Further investigation uncovers evidence suggesting that the victim was poisoned, leading CID to conclude that the apparent heart attack was, in fact, a murder orchestrated by someone with malicious intent.


Show name: CID
Starcast: Shivaji Satam, Dayanand Shetty, Aditya Srivastav

Episode Number: 820

About CID: 
-----------------
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam]. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

snippet.title: Navratri 2024 | Aigiri Nandini With Meaning in Hindi | Mahishasur Mardini Stotra | Madhubanti Bagchi
snippet.description:
Tilak Originals Presents, Aigiri Nandini, a beautiful version of the Mahishasura Mardini Stotram With Hindi Translataion. This captivating Stotram is Sung by Madhubanti Bagchi and brought to life with amazing music by Siddharth Amit Bhavsar, this Stotram is all about the fierce and loving spirit of Maa Durga.

As you listen, you'll not only enjoy the powerful melodies but also find Hindi translations that make the meaning come alive! It‚Äôs a perfect way to connect with the strength and grace of the Goddess Durga as she fights against darkness and evil.

With Navratri upon us, we want to wish you all a joyful celebration! May Maa Durga bless you with happiness, strength, and positivity during these special days.

Let‚Äôs celebrate together! Happy Navratri! Jai Maa Durga! ‚ú®

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta.
